{"tid":593851,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"樂視收皮,now揾邊個評述英超?","createTime":"2018-03-15T10:37:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-15T15:59:32.000Z","uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e55276d819a87c07d44a617fe748313ed72599f6","tid":593851,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T10:37:58.000Z","msg":"宜家now果D評述基本上講哂西甲wo...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a28ede060e242b9cf025b0be32109c7bacf0919e","tid":593851,"uid":2161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T10:38:32.000Z","msg":"照播 但得英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c51ac22dcda73b5642387929fe64cbde5e67196c","tid":593851,"uid":170821,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T10:40:56.000Z","msg":"<strong>【樂視熄燈】NowTV繼續直播英超 肯定不會接手NBA</strong><br />\n<br />\n樂視將於今晚「落閘」，與樂視合播英超的NowTV，收費電視業務主管蔡煒健今日在奧海城出席Now TV「全城撐」世界盃活動時，就此事作出回應，本周起的英超會如常進行，亦暗示日後會繼續直播英超賽事，但肯定不會接手NBA事宜。<br />\n<br />\n蔡煒健表示：「我們經過內部資源調配，本周六、日的四場英超直播會如常進行，會有廣東話評述，由現在起我們會接受英超的製作。」蔡煒健表示現在只是臨時安排，現仍跟樂視協商中，關於樂視客戶轉台至Now TV的費用，亦會盡快公佈，但肯定會有轉台優惠，他表示若樂視客戶想以最快方法申請Now足球app，亦已為此批客戶微調，實際費用會盡快公佈。他說：「價錢是調低了，希望可以幫到樂視客戶。」<ins>樂視評述員安排上，蔡煒健表示NowTV有足夠的評述人手，會用自己的評述員負責英超評述。</ins><br />\n<br />\n關於樂視跟ELP英超簽了三年合約，Now TV是否會接受，蔡煒健表示：「這方面，我真的答不到你，這是樂視同英超直接安排，必須要問樂視那邊；但以Now同英超多年合作，我們有信心未來會繼續播到英超賽事。」<br />\n<br />\n至於NBA方面，蔡煒健坦言：「由於NBA是樂視播影權持有人，我們不可以有任何評論，但我們沒有跟樂視談NBA的事。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180315/57951001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180315%2F57951001&d=rqW3Wev6K7EAcOQsoXcOev7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=3bbf5fbe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180315%2F57951001&h=41ebcdd0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180315/57951001</a>"},{"pid":"dbd79474f37454b77375d992f492d27e15abd035","tid":593851,"uid":91321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T10:43:36.000Z","msg":"呀巢加招積<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dca1acfa6133b09783c9b8f370122cc21422e314","tid":593851,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T10:50:23.000Z","msg":"now啲評述仲撚廢"},{"pid":"ed6714641906ade68b450f04cde1b46d610b117f","tid":593851,"uid":13774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T10:52:00.000Z","msg":"陳葦如 幾好"},{"pid":"e791ab6ebd5a37ad83afbf204d8ae63319c70362","tid":593851,"uid":33770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed6714641906ade68b450f04cde1b46d610b117f","tid":593851,"uid":13774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T10:52:00.000Z","msg":"陳葦如 幾好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T10:54:04.000Z","msg":"場場都佢講咪好"},{"pid":"879c3dcb3e10548ad4b65c4bab53653e4100fd76","tid":593851,"uid":9548,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T11:02:02.000Z","msg":"請返丘仔同ricky啦"},{"pid":"ee0746a6baf0bb0686fd238249dab98f0ca60125","tid":593851,"uid":22948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dca1acfa6133b09783c9b8f370122cc21422e314","tid":593851,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T10:50:23.000Z","msg":"now啲評述仲撚廢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T15:19:59.000Z","msg":"agger 其實樂視啲講波佬算係咁<br />\n畢竟行頭細 出名既幾乎都係曬樂視"},{"pid":"9e0909222fdb44986df0b01e3ae58b69a1e02453","tid":593851,"uid":164608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T15:21:01.000Z","msg":"我唔要文彼德條垃圾呀屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/